hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 对于等熵、量热完全气体混合物，其驻点温度与静温之比为
$$\frac{T_0}{T}=1+\frac{\gamma_{\rm mix}-1}{2}\,M^2\,. $$  
2. 各组分的质量比热为
$$c_{p,i}=\frac{\gamma_i}{\gamma_i-1}\,\frac{R_u}{M_i},\quad
c_{v,i}=\frac{1}{\gamma_i-1}\,\frac{R_u}{M_i}\,,\quad i=1,2.$$  
3. 混合物的比热（基于质量）为
$$c_{p,\rm mix}=c_1c_{p,1}+c_2c_{p,2}
=R_u\Bigl(\frac{c_1\gamma_1}{(\gamma_1-1)M_1}+\frac{c_2\gamma_2}{(\gamma_2-1)M_2}\Bigr),$$  
$$c_{v,\rm mix}=c_1c_{v,1}+c_2c_{v,2}
=R_u\Bigl(\frac{c_1}{(\gamma_1-1)M_1}+\frac{c_2}{(\gamma_2-1)M_2}\Bigr).$$  
因此
$$\gamma_{\rm mix}=\frac{c_{p,\rm mix}}{c_{v,\rm mix}}\,,\qquad
\gamma_{\rm mix}-1=\frac{c_{p,\rm mix}-c_{v,\rm mix}}{c_{v,\rm mix}}
=\frac{R_u\bigl(\frac{c_1}{M_1}+\frac{c_2}{M_2}\bigr)}{R_u\bigl(\frac{c_1}{(\gamma_1-1)M_1}+\frac{c_2}{(\gamma_2-1)M_2}\bigr)}  
=\frac{\frac{c_1}{M_1}+\frac{c_2}{M_2}}{\frac{c_1}{(\gamma_1-1)M_1}+\frac{c_2}{(\gamma_2-1)M_2}}\,. $$  
4. 代入等熵关系式可得
$$\frac{T_0}{T}
=1+\frac{M^2}{2}\;\frac{\displaystyle\frac{c_1}{M_1}+\frac{c_2}{M_2}}
{\displaystyle\frac{c_1}{(\gamma_1-1)M_1}+\frac{c_2}{(\gamma_2-1)M_2}}\,. $$

我们从等熵体积模量的定义开始
$$K \;=\;\rho\Bigl(\frac{\partial p}{\partial\rho}\Bigr)_s
\;=\;K_0 + n\,p
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
\frac{dp}{d\rho}=\frac{K_0+n\,p}{\rho}.$$
从 $(p,\rho)$ 积分到 $(p_0,\rho_0)$，
$$\int_{p}^{p_0}\frac{dp}{K_0+n\,p}
=\int_{\rho}^{\rho_0}\frac{d\rho}{\rho}
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
\ln\frac{\rho_0}{\rho}
=\frac{1}{n}\ln\frac{K_0+n\,p_0}{K_0+n\,p}
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
\frac{\rho_0}{\rho}
=\Bigl[\frac{K_0+n\,p_0}{K_0+n\,p}\Bigr]^{\!1/n}.$$
接下来，正压流体的滞止焓关系给出
$$h_0-h=\frac{u^2}{2}
\quad\text{with}\quad dh=\frac{dp}{\rho}
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
\int_{p}^{p_0}\frac{dp}{\rho}
=\frac{u^2}{2}.$$
沿着等熵线将 $\rho$ 表示为 $p$ 的函数：
$$\rho(p')=\frac{\rho}{(K_0+n\,p)^{1/n}}\,(K_0+n\,p')^{1/n},$$
所以
$$\frac{1}{\rho(p')}
=\frac{(K_0+n\,p)^{1/n}}{\rho\,(K_0+n\,p')^{1/n}}.$$
因此
$$\frac{u^2}{2}
=\frac{(K_0+n\,p)^{1/n}}{\rho}\,
\frac{1}{n-1}\Bigl[(K_0+n\,p_0)^{\frac{n-1}{n}}-(K_0+n\,p)^{\frac{n-1}{n}}\Bigr].
$$
使用 $a^2=K/\rho=(K_0+n\,p)/\rho$ 和 
$K_0+n\,p_0=\rho a^2(\rho_0/\rho)^n$，简化后可得
$$\frac{u^2}{2}
=\frac{a^2}{n-1}\Bigl[(\tfrac{\rho_0}{\rho})^{n-1}-1\Bigr],
\quad M^2=\frac{u^2}{a^2}
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
M^2=\frac{2}{n-1}\Bigl[(\tfrac{\rho_0}{\rho})^{n-1}-1\Bigr].$$
求解 $\rho_0/\rho$ 可得
$$\Bigl(\frac{\rho_0}{\rho}\Bigr)^{n-1}
=1+\frac{n-1}{2}M^2
\;\;\Longrightarrow\;\;
\frac{\rho_0}{\rho}
=\Bigl(1+\tfrac{n-1}{2}M^2\Bigr)^{\!1/(n-1)}.$$
